title: 38th ANNUAL FANTASY EXTRAVAGANZA
itunes:title: 38th ANNUAL FANTASY EXTRAVAGANZA
description:
Welcome to the most anticipated show of the year - the 38th annual FANTASY EXTRAVAGANZA! Dan Hanzus and Gregg Rosenthal entertain a lineup as never seen before! We hit sleepers and busts with the Big Fish, Evan Silva, himself (5:16), receivers and tight ends with Marcas Grant (26:48), quarterbacks with RotoPat (43:16), and running backs with Liz Loza (1:06:57).
